1547676669.text: "We show that sunitinib treatment does not inhibit EGF induced EGFR phosphorylation, confirming the specificity of sunitinib to block PDGFR activation, and as a result, prevents PDGF-BB mediated transactivation of EGFR (XREF_FIG)."
